Replace lawETP boost and create 365 BCH/flexUSD vault.

&nbsp; 

 Expected impact

1.Some more BCH/flexUSD will flow in to the DEX and volatility will generate more fees for our treasury. Since it's a 365 vault this liquidity will stay here for long not just drain EmberSwap and sell for a fast profit.

&nbsp; 

2. Every 21th use the fees on flexUSD/BCH with EMBER from treasury to create flexUSD/EMBER and BCH/EMBER LP's. 

&nbsp; 

Impact on users

1. Users will see EmberSwap becoming more sustainable/stable if not bullish.

&nbsp; 

2. lawETP with about 400$ liquidity will stop draining EmberSwap.
